00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,000
Arrange them properly.

287
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:22,800
Yes, sir.

288
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:24,840
Count them quickly.

289
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,600
I'm back.

290
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,960
Magistrate, you're back.

291
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:33,320
This

292
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,120
is listed by Hong.

293
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,640
Take a look
and see if anything is missing.

294
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:39,600
The rest of the properties
have already been prepared

295
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,480
and sent to the pawn shop.

296
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,000
What's the rush?

297
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:44,160
The directive says
to report for duty immediately.

298
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,360
You have to prepare early.

299
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:47,560
All right.

300
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,520
Hong, you make the arrangements.

301
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,040
Huaiying.

302
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:54,520
Haven't you

303
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,240
told Miss Cao about us leaving?

304
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,880
When are you planning to do it?

305
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:02,720
I know.

306
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,800
You are afraid
if you tell her about us leaving,

307
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:06,000
she won't go with us, right?

308
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:09,640
I will tell her.

309
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:10,680
I will.

310
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:13,120
Magistrate, you're back.

311
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,680
Hong.

312
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,480
If I seriously consider leaving,

313
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:22,360
it is not easy inside.

314
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,440
What is not easy?

315
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:25,720
Penglai...

316
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,920
I have had enough.

317
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:29,360
Especially the weather,

318
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,360
it rains and rains and rains.

319
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:33,520
I almost forget what the sun looks like.

320
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:35,440
When we arrive at Lanfang County
in the desert,

321
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:37,040
we're going to have a tough time
with all the wind and sun.

322
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:37,960
That will not make it easier.

323
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,040
Better than this humid weather.

324
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:40,800
Days after days,

325
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:42,280
I can't get my clothes dry.

326
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:45,320
Since we are definitely
going to Lanfang,

327
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:47,320
and we are still now in Penglai,

328
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,000
do well what is at hand.

329
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,680
Don't always be restless.

330
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,800
Particularly you.

331
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,120
Quickly count this.

332
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,280
Particularly you.

333
00:16:58,800 --> 00:16:59,840
Mind your own business.

334
00:17:27,060 --> 00:17:28,180
[Pawn ticket]

335
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:36,160
This feather...

336
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,560
This beak...

337
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:39,120
And these clothes.

338
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,720
Exactly Rain Master.

339
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,120
That means

340
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:46,400
Huang Ying'er lives in the watchtower.

341
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,800
And the body of Mr. Zhong

342
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:50,960
was also found in the watchtower.

343
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:52,680
All of this

344
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,840
can't just be a coincidence, can it?

345
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,080
Magistrate.

346
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:59,000
Should we arrest Huang Ying'er first

347
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,720
and interrogate her slowly?

348
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:01,400
Huang Ying'er

349
00:18:01,760 --> 00:18:02,920
is not an ordinary person.

350
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:04,480
That won't work.

351
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,400
Tomorrow morning,

352
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:07,760
I will go meet her.

353
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,000
May I ask if the Magistrate is here?

354
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:25,840
What do you want with Magistrate?

355
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,680
Miss Cao asked me
to deliver this improved straw rain cape.

356
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:29,640
And give it to Magistrate Di.

357
00:18:30,120 --> 00:18:31,520
Magistrate said he doesn't need it.

358
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:32,800
Take it back.

359
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:34,440
Well...

360
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:43,360
Give it to me.

361
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:50,200
Where is Ma Rong?

362
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:52,350
I don't know.

363
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:55,640
Since she knew we were leaving Penglai,

364
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:57,400
her mind has already been elsewhere.

365
00:18:57,830 --> 00:19:00,070
I don't know where she's now.

366
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:29,080
Thanks.

367
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,320
The straw rain cape is well woven.

368
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,000
It's quite comfortable for me to wear.

369
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,960
You give this to him

370
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:54,440
just to remind him

371
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:55,760
of coming and seeing you more often, huh?

372
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,400
Unfortunately,

373
00:19:58,560 --> 00:19:59,680
he's busy with the investigation.

374
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,240
So I came on his behalf.

375
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:03,440
What?

376
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,560
You don't want me here?

377
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:06,920
He is the Magistrate.

378
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,320
As he's investigating a case,

379
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:10,040
he must be focused.

380
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,880
I'll wait for him.

381
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:25,480
No wonder he likes you.

382
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:27,160
If I were a man,

383
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:29,280
maybe I would fall in love with you too.

384
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,080
But I came today

385
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:34,960
to kindly advise you

386
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,240
to stop waiting.

387
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:38,920
Magistrate no longer needs
a straw rain cape.

388
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:41,000
Because soon

389
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:42,280
we will go to a place

390
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:44,040
where it never rains.

391
