[Zhong's]

392
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:22,280
Shopkeeper Lin, what are you doing?

393
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:22,880
Step aside!

394
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:25,000
Put it back! Put it back!

395
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,560
Don't take it away! Don't take it away!

396
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,160
Move aside!

397
00:21:28,040 --> 00:21:28,960
What's going on?

