00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:31,080
Magistrate.

399
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,040
Sir.

400
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:34,320
Zhong Fang has already handed over

401
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,600
this shop to our shopkeeper.

