00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,400
We're here to move some things away.

403
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,040
Go!

404
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:38,640
No way.

405
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:39,040
Magistrate.

406
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:40,320
Our master wouldn't do this.

407
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:42,200
